        <num>CCP 428</num>
        <heading>428.  No abatement on death of party</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 428.  No abatement on death of party
An action does not abate on the death of a party.  The only exception to this rule is an action to enforce a right or obligation which is strictly personal.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
